title: V-Kitpater Silicone Spatula Set for Cooking Baking and Mixing, Food Grade Rubber Spatulas, High Heat Resistant for Nonstick Cookware, Dishwasher Safe BPA-Free, Multicolor Kitchen Utensils, Pack of 5

Stronger & More Flexible: The silicone kitchen utensils set are built-in iron core technology, they are sturdy enough to bear pressure and soft enough to reach side of bowl. The strong iron won't break easy like cheap plastic spatula, Right -angle+rounded scrape design, easy scraping on both sides, it is best for cooking baking mixing and scraping.
